{"about_the_game":"In the On Pixels game the goal is to leave all the lights on at the same time, using the minimum amount of movements for this.<br><br>The levels were carefully done one by one and balanced with a good progression of difficulty.<br><br>There are 5 game modes, with 6 boards each mode, and 10 parts on each board. Resulting in 5 x 6 x 10 = 300 levels for you to challenge your reasoning.<br><br>Can you turn on all the lights using the fewest movements possible?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>FEATURES</strong></h2>The game features art made in pixel art, using the PICO-8 color palette.<br><br>The songs are relaxing and provide a pleasant experience for the player.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>HOW TO PLAY</strong></h2>The Yellow Light affects itself and the lights immediately below, above, the left and the right of itself.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397540/extras/yellow600.gif?t=1605556634\" /><br><br>The Horizontal Pink Light affects itself and the lights immediately in the left and in the right of itself.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397540/extras/pinkH600.gif?t=1605556634\" /><br><br>The Vertical Pink Light affects itself and the lights immediately below and above of itself.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397540/extras/pinkV600.gif?t=1605556634\" /><br><br>The Blue Light affects itself and the lights immediately below, above, the left and the right of itself, and in all its diagonals.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397540/extras/blue600.gif?t=1605556634\" /><br><br>The Horizontal Red Light affects itself and all the lights in the left and in the right of itself.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397540/extras/redH600.gif?t=1605556634\" /><br><br>The Vertical Red Light affects itself and all the lights below and above of itself.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397540/extras/redV600.gif?t=1605556634\" /><br><br>The Orange Light affects itself and all the lights below, above, the left and the right of itself.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397540/extras/orange600.gif?t=1605556634\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The Yellow Light","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1397540/89814dda82df2a974607ea27e2f114d4102c116d.jpg"},{"name":"The Yellow Tiles","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1397540/0fc799733ed81368a95a4321528e32497b68758e.jpg"},{"name":"The Yellow ON Board","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1397540/59db71113f6eaa58da0a3feaec3f1b913e11fbfe.jpg"},{"name":"The Yellow PIXEL Board","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1397540/706c34949bf58d3bcef6912a736d22dbb8298663.jpg"},{"name":"The Yellow Sun","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1397540/a7d47b0baf113617ed42bd7bdf2b693de45eb73e.jpg"},{"name":"The Yellow Moon","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1397540/11b4d46ba3b98bbc953477e3c35ae41be99685ac.jpg"},{"name":"The Yellow Slightly Smiling Face","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1397540/8150a275fce8f3abd5985e871913e2db6ac89d8b.jpg"},{"name":"The Yellow Grinning Face with Smiling Eyes","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1397540/f010a27af675c2f261d399a60931ad8d01350724.jpg"},{"name":"The Yellow Brick Road","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/13975